    "title": "Immediate Requirement Production Engineer at H.B. Fuller India",
    "description": "We at H.B. Fuller India are looking for an experienced Production Engineer based out of Varanasi. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout H.B. Fuller India:\nH.B. Fuller India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Quality Control\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with H.B. Fuller India!",
